show.description: "From Zero to Hero" is a drama that follows the inspiring journey of an ordinary young man who rises from humble beginnings to achieve remarkable success through hard work, resilience, and determination. Blending elements of sports, motivation, and personal growth, the story emphasizes the value of perseverance in the face of challenges. The drama showcases emotional relationships, life lessons, and the transformation of the protagonist from an underdog to a celebrated figure.
